        <article class="sb-meta-wave-landing__problem-card">
          <div class="sb-meta-wave-landing__problem-number font-caption weight-bold">02</div>
          <h3 class="sb-meta-wave-landing__card-title font-body weight-bold">Muddy sound</h3>
          <p class="sb-meta-wave-landing__card-body font-body weight-regular">
            Consumer earbuds are tuned to sound impressive in a store with boosted bass and scooped mids. The mix you're hearing is not the mix your audience hears.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="sb-meta-wave-landing__problem-card">
          <div class="sb-meta-wave-landing__problem-number font-caption weight-bold">03</div>
          <h3 class="sb-meta-wave-landing__card-title font-body weight-bold">Zero isolation</h3>
          <p class="sb-meta-wave-landing__card-body font-body weight-regular">
